
---

start:			ec_mon_control start

start (after a crash):	ec_mon_control -f start

stop:			ec_mon_control stop

---

control tool:			ec_mon_control

master daemon:			ec_mon_master

check files:			ec_mon_check

monitoring task starter:	ec_mon_monitor_task_submit

monitoring task wrapper:	ec_mon_monitor_task_wrapper

archiving old runs:		ec_mon_archive

cleanup root files w/o status	ec_mon_cleanup_root

library of subroutines:		ec_mon_utils.pl

---

init script used to restart 
ec_mon_master after reboot:	ec_mon_master.init

cron job used to reset the
mon_run flag after reboot:	ec_mon_monitor_task_watcher

cron job used to fix long
standing daq_run flag:		ec_mon_daq_watcher

